What are you doing with that TV?

872
01:12:12.220 --> 01:12:14.738
- Hi. Want a ride?
- No, thanks.

873
01:12:28.859 --> 01:12:30.338
Hey, did you two hear the news...

874
01:12:30.499 --> 01:12:31.939
- on the radio?
- No.

875
01:12:32.100 --> 01:12:34.939
- A riot's broken out downtown.
- How come?

876
01:12:35.100 --> 01:12:36.818
Who knows how these things
get started?

877
01:12:36.979 --> 01:12:39.138
Attention! All cadets report immediately...

878
01:12:39.299 --> 01:12:40.859
to the parking lot in full riot gear.

879
01:12:41.020 --> 01:12:44.859
