to the parking lot in full riot gear.

880
01:12:45.019 --> 01:12:46.138
This is not a drill.

881
01:12:46.299 --> 01:12:49.018
- Jones! Was that you?
- No, man.

882
01:12:49.740 --> 01:12:52.619
Let's go, let's go, let's go!

883
01:12:52.780 --> 01:12:57.299
Get out there fast!
Move it, move it, move it!

884
01:12:57.980 --> 01:12:59.379
Let's go, let's go.

885
01:13:12.459 --> 01:13:16.099
This is it. This is the big one.

886
01:13:16.820 --> 01:13:18.498
It's time this cop...

887
01:13:18.659 --> 01:13:20.739
met the public.

888
01:13:26.299 --> 01:13:29.819
