896
01:13:48.539 --> 01:13:52.218
Tackleberry, do you understand,
numb nuts?

897
01:13:52.379 --> 01:13:53.858
Yes, sir.

898
01:14:01.380 --> 01:14:03.098
Come on!

899
01:14:07.579 --> 01:14:10.099
We are now entering
the expressway at Belmont.

900
01:14:10.660 --> 01:14:13.498
