on Sixteenth Street...

901
01:14:13.659 --> 01:14:15.538
between 4th and 8th Avenues.

902
01:14:15.699 --> 01:14:17.939
Sixteenth Street? Are you sure, sir?

903
01:14:18.100 --> 01:14:20.459
Of course I'm sure.
I never forget a number.

904
01:14:21.739 --> 01:14:22.978
Yes, sir.

905
01:14:23.140 --> 01:14:24.979
