Which one do we do first?

1007
01:25:11.460 --> 01:25:13.219
I believe I'd shoot this one.

1008
01:25:13.380 --> 01:25:14.579
Yeah, the old one.

1009
01:25:23.419 --> 01:25:27.859
- Looks like cadet revolvers to me.
- I know those guys.

1010
01:25:31.740 --> 01:25:34.658
Don't move, dirtbag!

1011
01:25:59.899 --> 01:26:02.019
Hey. Hey, hey.

1012
01:26:02.180 --> 01:26:04.178
- Hey, hey, hey.
- What's wrong with this man?

1013
01:26:04.339 --> 01:26:06.898
There was gunplay, sir, and he missed it.

1014
01:26:17.619 --> 01:26:21.058
- Lieutenant Harris? Captain Reed.
- Nice to meet you, sir.

1015
01:26:21.220 --> 01:26:24.218
Thank you. I also want to thank you
for looking out for Mahoney.

1016
01:26:24.380 --> 01:26:26.699
It was an honor and a pleasure, sir.

1017
01:26:26.860 --> 01:26:28.819
Thank you, sir.

1018
01:26:35.380 --> 01:26:37.338
- Could you just...?
- This woman bothering you?

1019
01:26:37.499 --> 01:26:40.419
What? No. This is my mother.

1020
01:26:41.619 --> 01:26:43.859
Ten-four. Carry on.

1021
01:26:44.020 --> 01:26:45.738
- Oh, my precious...
- Mom, would...?

1022
01:26:46.100 --> 01:26:48.178
- Then at 8:00 you'll meet my mother.
- Right.

1023
01:26:48.339 --> 01:26:50.778
- You'd better have some flowers.
- Flowers, check.

1024
01:26:54.580 --> 01:26:55.979
You men, stop that.

1025
01:27:00.139 --> 01:27:02.018
Oh, well.

1026
01:27:02.179 --> 01:27:03.779
That's more like it, Mahoney.

1027
01:27:04.539 --> 01:27:06.818
Good man. Keep up the good work.

1028
01:27:07.460 --> 01:27:08.859
Thank you, sir.

1029
01:27:09.019 --> 01:27:13.059
Ladies and gentlemen, the commandant
of the Academy, Eric Lassard.

1030
01:27:19.540 --> 01:27:22.819
So many unusual events have happened
to this graduating class...

1031
01:27:22.980 --> 01:27:24.619
and to me also.

1032
01:27:24.780 --> 01:27:28.098
I could tell you many, many stories,
but instead...

1033
01:27:28.259 --> 01:27:30.379
I have a presentation to make.

1034
01:27:30.540 --> 01:27:33.939
No Academy cadet has ever received
the highest award...

1035
01:27:34.100 --> 01:27:35.979
this police department has to make.

1036
01:27:36.459 --> 01:27:38.498
Today, there are two.

1037
01:27:38.659 --> 01:27:41.899
Officers Moses Hightower...

1038
01:27:42.740 --> 01:27:44.619
and Carey Mahoney.

1039
01:27:44.780 --> 01:27:46.939
Gentlemen, please step forward.

1040
01:28:21.059 --> 01:28:23.378
You are both expected
to make a few short remarks.

1041
01:28:26.460 --> 01:28:28.858
Officer Hightower.

1042
01:28:34.300 --> 01:28:35.738
Thanks.

1043
01:28:38.100 --> 01:28:40.859
That was very, very, very good.

1044
01:28:41.339 --> 01:28:43.258
Officer Mahoney.

1045
01:28:48.459 --> 01:28:51.579
Thank you, Commandant Lassard,
Chief Hurnst...

1046
01:28:51.739 --> 01:28:54.098
Madam Mayor, Mr. President...

1047
01:28:54.259 --> 01:28:57.658
His Holiness the Pope,
the King of Norway...

1048
01:28:57.819 --> 01:28:59.738
and our other honored guests.
